'''[[uranium]] [[hexafluoride]]'''
#{{chemistry}} a [[binary compound]] of uranium and [[fluorine]], UF<sub>6</sub>; it is a grey solid, or heavy gas, and is used in the [[uranium enrichment]] process to produce [[fuel]] for [[nuclear reactor]]s or [[nuclear weapon]]s

